column5: Just back from Pinfalls Lots of 20" fish going
Just back from Pinefalls , the bite is great best fished only 27 1/2" , lots of 20"-23" fish going ( 50 fish days )
Just back from Pinefalls , the bite is great best fished only 27 1/2" , lots of 20"-23" fish going ( 50 fish days )

Just to comment, it seems there is a real strong class of the 20-23" fish in the system. This should start to produce some really nice trophy fish in around 4-5 years, maybe sooner. We were up in early October and just hammered the 21" fish. We hope these fish make it strong past the slot so they can grow big!! The 21" fish we were catching were footballs fat as can be!
